Paper: hep-th/9906074

Date: 1999-06-09

Title: Entropy from the foam

Comments: Revtex 3.0, 15 pages, accepted in Phys.Lett. B

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B459 (1999) 461-467

A simple model of spacetime foam, made by N wormholes in a semiclassicalapproximation, is taken under examination. We show that the Bekenstein-Hawkingentropy is here ``quantized'' in agreement with the heuristic calculation ofBekenstein.